#: ../extras/knowledge-base.rst:226
msgid ""
"As soon as the knowledge base contains one or more answers, you can use "
"these just like text modules. Instead of :kbd:`:`:kbd:`:` just use :kbd:`?"
"`:kbd:`?` to open the search modal. The search is done full text on both "
"answer body and title in all languages available. If you've found what "
"you've been looking for, simply press :kbd:`Enter` to load the answer into "
"the ticket article. The inserted content does not replace the article's "
"content but is inserted at the cursor's position."
msgstr ""
